Biography

AT WASHINGTON

2024: Enrolled at UW in time to participate in spring football.

AT SAN JOSE STATE & HIGH SCHOOL

Played the 2021 through 2023 seasons at San Jose State ... honorable mention All-Mountain West as a junior in 2023, when he led the Spartans with 106 tackles ... second in the Mountain West with 60 solo tackles ... made 12 tackles in SJSU's Hawai'i Bowl vs. Coastal Carolina ... had 12 tackles and two fumble recoveries vs. Boise State in 2023 ... had 93 tackles as a sophomore in 2022 ... career-high 14 stops vs. Utah State ... played in seven games as a true freshman in 2021 ... made 19 tackles in 2021 ... two-time CalHiSports.com all-state selection at Long Beach Poly ... named to the first team in 2020 (spring of 2021) and the third team in 2019 ... made 27 tackles in just four games in the pandemic-shortened 2020 season, when he was also Moore League Defensive MVP and All-CIF Southern Section Division II first team ... as a high-school junior in 2019, made 102 tackles in 12 games and was named to the All-Moore League first team ... played for coach Stephen Barbee at Long Beach Poly.
